description:
In my career I learned that in time, dance evolved and you, as a dancer, will have to keep pushing yourself to the limits.

In this dancers generation is not enough just to dance, you will need to amaze your audience by making your dance look “impossible”.

In this course you will learn how to perform the knee moonwalk, also called the back slide on your knees.

I will teach you step by step how to perform these moves, with detailed explanation so even a beginner can understand the concept that stands behind this dancing move.

The knee moonwalk is not just a dancing move.

Is has history for more than 20 years and if you perform it at the right time and place, your audience will be amazed.
title: Learn How To Back Slide On Your Knees (Knee Moonwalking)
